General.Name: Sprintex Limited
General.Description: Sprintex Limited, together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and distributes clean air compressors. Its clean air compressors comprise superchargers and supercharger systems. The company also provides customer support, as well as sales and marketing services. It operates in the United States, Australia, the United Arab Emirates, and internationally. The company was incorporated in 2003 and is based in Perth, Australia.
